title: Djoj Center
description: This all vegetarian cafe is open to the public on Thursday evenings for dinner and offers a vegan set dinner on request. Offers a multitude of courses, activities, and trainings on topics such as massage, meditation, dance, yoga, bodywork, coaching and more which vary in duration. If you take courses here, the cafe is open for veg meals daily. The venue is also used for a variety of veg events so check the schedule.
